'''什鲁斯伯里伯爵'''（Earl of Shrewsbury，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|ʃ|r|oʊ|z|b|ər|i}}<ref>不是{{IPAc-en|ˈ|ʃ|r|uː|z|b|ər|i}}. --''Debrett's'' ''Correct Form'', 2002 edition</ref>）是英格兰的一个世袭制[[伯爵|伯爵]]爵位，历史上总共创建过两次，第二次建立于1442年，并传承至今。什鲁斯伯里伯爵还同时拥有爱尔兰爵位沃特福德伯爵（Earl of Waterford）和大不列颠爵位{{le|塔尔伯特伯爵|Earl Talbot}}。什鲁斯伯里伯爵是英格兰最古老的伯爵爵位之一。<ref>{{cite news|title=Earl|url=https://www.debretts.com/expertise/essential-guide-to-the-peerage/ranks-and-privileges-of-the-peerage/earl/|publisher=Debrett's|accessdate=2020-12-28|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230195613/https://www.debretts.com/expertise/essential-guide-to-the-peerage/ranks-and-privileges-of-the-peerage/earl/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.debretts.com/expertise/essential-guide-to-the-peerage/ranks-and-privileges-of-the-peerage/duke/|title=Duke - Debrett's|work=Debrett's|access-date=2017-03-28|language=en-GB|archive-date=2017-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216131611/https://www.debretts.com/expertise/essential-guide-to-the-peerage/ranks-and-privileges-of-the-peerage/duke/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

